==English==

===Etymology===
Derivation uncertain; one suggestion is Latin [[manustuprare]].

===Verb===
{{en-verb|masturbat|ing}}

# [[self]] [[stimulate]] [[sexually]], usually with a hand or hands.
# to have sex by yourself, esp. by use of one’s hand, sometimes with a partner.

